  <brief_title>Enteral Glutamine in Neurologically-injured Patients</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Placebo-controlled Clinical Trial of Enteral Glutamine Supplementation in Neurologically-injured Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
